<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA101">
<l>uraiyiṉā limmālai yantāti veṇpāk</l>
<l>karaiviṉāṟ kāraikkāṟ pēycol - paravuvā</l>
<l>rārāta vaṉpiṉō ṭaṇṇalaicceṉ ṟēttuvār</l>
<l>pērāta kātal piṟantu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This garland [made] from words as an Antāti in Veṇpā,</l>
<l>those who spread/rever the words of the demoness of Kāraikkāl in tenderness</l>
<l>will go [and] praise the majesty with insatiable love,</l>
<l>being born with immovable love.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
